But if you do have the radio on,
it's a great opportunity

00:22:12.260 --> 00:22:15.480
to try and download as
much as you can.

00:22:15.480 --> 00:22:17.600
So we've been talking about
doing everything anonymously,

00:22:17.600 --> 00:22:18.290
which is great.

00:22:18.290 --> 00:22:19.920
It has some real advantages.

00:22:19.920 --> 00:22:22.130
But there are always advantages
to actually knowing

00:22:22.130 --> 00:22:23.850
